status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Target groups 3 and 4 in the summary of the 1st INCF Workshop on Needs for
 Training in Neuroinformatics (2008)
\end_layout

\end_inset

) interested in learning best practices in the use and development of reproducib
le research tools.
 The target audience are researchers with some programming experience in
 Python, C/C++, or Matlab.
 The course will admit 30 participants, to maintain a good instructor/student
 ratio.
 In particular, we will seek to make the course available to members of
 groups under-represented in neuroinformatics.
